OL,3,CChloe Meadows so 'scared' she ignored
OL,4,Culcerative colitis symptoms for a
OL,5,Cdecade
OL,7,FReality TV star Chloe Meadows has said
OL,8,Fshe was so "scared" of the doctors and
OL,9,Fthe prospect of "having any procedure
OL,10,Fdone" that she ignored symptoms of a
OL,11,Fchronic inflammatory bowel condition
OL,12,Ffor around 10 years.
OL,14,FThe former star of The Only Way Is
OL,15,FEssex, 33, first discovered blood in
OL,16,Fher stool, a symptom of ulcerative
OL,17,Fcolitis, when she was 16.
