OL,3,CChloe Meadows so 'scared' she ignored
OL,4,Culcerative colitis symptoms for a
OL,5,Cdecade
OL,7,F"I went to a college where I boarded
OL,8,Fwhen I was 16. I was staying away from
OL,9,Fhome and I was living in a student
OL,10,Fhouse and there was blood down the
OL,11,Ftoilet", she told Dr Oscar Duke's
OL,12,FBedside Manners podcast.
OL,14,F"I remember I told my mum and I was
OL,15,Flike, there's quite a lot of blood
OL,16,Fdown the toilet. I'm not really sure
OL,17,Fwhat's going on.
OL,19,FMeadows added: "At this point in my
OL,20,Flife, I had never really ever been to
OL,21,Fthe hospital. I'd never been sick.
