OL,7,F"I got this letter, and this is awful,
OL,8,Fbut I got this letter and I just never
OL,9,Fwent to the appointment because I was
OL,10,Fterrified.
OL,12,F"It would stop for periods of time so
OL,13,Fthat the blood would go away. I'd be
OL,14,Flike, 'Oh, cool, it's gone away, I'm
OL,15,Fbetter. There's nothing wrong with me'.
OL,17,F"I'd go through years where it
OL,18,Fwouldn't happen and then it would
OL,19,Fhappen again, and then it would stop
OL,20,Fagain.
