OL,5,Cdecade
OL,7,F"I just got on with it and ignored it.
OL,8,FI think I was scared of having any
OL,9,Fprocedure done.
OL,11,F"I was also scared of what they were
OL,12,Fgoing to tell me ... I was just
OL,13,Fterrified, which is not really a
OL,14,Freason not to go to the doctor, but I
OL,15,Fthink that's just what I thought.
OL,17,FUlcerative colitis is a long-term
OL,18,Fcondition where the colon and rectum
OL,19,Fbecome inflamed, according to the NHS
OL,20,Fwebsite.
