OL,3,CChloe Meadows so 'scared' she ignored
OL,4,Culcerative colitis symptoms for a
OL,5,Cdecade
OL,7,FWhile she was out filming, after she
OL,8,Fhad the blood tests, Meadows received
OL,9,Fa number of missed calls from her
OL,10,Ffather who then texted her to say a
OL,11,Fdoctor had advised her she should got
OL,12,Fstraight to A&E because her "blood was
OL,13,Fso low".
OL,15,F"I went to the hospital. I had to have
OL,16,Fall of these checks and these iron
OL,17,Finfusions and that was where it
OL,18,Fstarted," she said.
